    If `x < 1`, the function returns `NaN`.

    Parameters
    ----------
    x: number
        Input value.

    Returns
    -------
    y: number
        Hyperbolic arccosecant (in radians).

    Examples
    --------
    > var y = {{alias}}( 0 )
    NaN
    > y = {{alias}}( -1.0 )
    ~-0.881
